<p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify;"><font face="Verdana"><span class="LineHeight1-5"><span style="font-size: 9pt;"> </span></span></font></p>
 <font face="Verdana"><span class="LineHeight1-5"> </span></font> 
<p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify;"><font face="Verdana" color="#262626"><span class="LineHeight1-5"><span style="font-size: 9pt;">1)<span style="font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-synthesis: weight style; font-variant: normal;">       </span></span><span style="font-size: 9pt;">Устав предприятия (копия)</span></span></font></p>
 <font color="#262626"> <font face="Verdana"><span class="LineHeight1-5"> </span></font> </font> 
<p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify;"><font face="Verdana" color="#262626"><span class="LineHeight1-5"><span style="font-size: 9pt;">2)<span style="font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-synthesis: weight style; font-variant: normal;">       </span></span><span style="font-size: 9pt;">Копию приказа о назначении директора</span></span></font></p>
 <font color="#262626"> <font face="Verdana"><span class="LineHeight1-5"> </span></font> </font> 
<p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify;"><font face="Verdana" color="#262626"><span class="LineHeight1-5"><span style="font-size: 9pt;">3)<span style="font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-synthesis: weight style; font-variant: normal;">       </span></span><span style="font-size: 9pt;">Свидетельство о внесении записи в Единый Государственный Реестр юридических лиц (копия)</span></span></font></p>
 <font color="#262626"> <font face="Verdana"><span class="LineHeight1-5"> </span></font> </font> 
<p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify;"><font face="Verdana" color="#262626"><span class="LineHeight1-5"><span style="font-size: 9pt;">4)<span style="font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-synthesis: weight style; font-variant: normal;">       </span></span><span style="font-size: 9pt;">Свидетельство о постановке предприятия на налоговый учет (копия)</span></span></font></p>
 <font color="#262626"> <font face="Verdana"><span class="LineHeight1-5"> </span></font> </font> 
<p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify;"><font face="Verdana" color="#262626"><span class="LineHeight1-5"><span style="font-size: 9pt;">5)<span style="font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-synthesis: weight style; font-variant: normal;">       </span></span><span style="font-size: 9pt;">Протокол учредителей предприятия об избрании генерального директора (копия)</span></span></font></p>
 <font color="#262626"> <font face="Verdana"><span class="LineHeight1-5"> </span></font> </font> 
<p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify;"><font face="Verdana" color="#262626"><span class="LineHeight1-5"><span style="font-size: 9pt;">6)<span style="font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-synthesis: weight style; font-variant: normal;">       </span></span><span style="font-size: 9pt;">Паспорт водителя (ей) (копия) включая страницу с пропиской</span></span></font></p>
 <font color="#262626"> <font face="Verdana"><span class="LineHeight1-5"> </span></font> </font> 
<p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify;"><font face="Verdana" color="#262626"><span class="LineHeight1-5"><span style="font-size: 9pt;">7)<span style="font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-synthesis: weight style; font-variant: normal;">       </span></span><span style="font-size: 9pt;">Копию паспорта транспортного средства</span></span></font></p>
 <font color="#262626"> <font face="Verdana"><span class="LineHeight1-5"> </span></font> </font> 
<p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify;"><font face="Verdana" color="#262626"><span class="LineHeight1-5"><span style="font-size: 9pt;">8)<span style="font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-synthesis: weight style; font-variant: normal;">       </span></span><span style="font-size: 9pt;">Копию свидетельства о регистрации транспортного средства</span></span></font></p>
 <font color="#262626"> <font face="Verdana"><span class="LineHeight1-5"> </span></font> </font> 
<p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify;"><font face="Verdana" color="#262626"><span class="LineHeight1-5"><span style="font-size: 9pt;">9)<span style="font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-synthesis: weight style; font-variant: normal;">       </span></span><span style="font-size: 9pt;">Копию водительского удостоверения.</span></span></font></p>
 <font color="#262626"> <font face="Verdana"><span class="LineHeight1-5"> </span></font> </font> 
<p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify;"><font face="Verdana" color="#262626"><span class="LineHeight1-5"><span style="font-size: 9pt;">10)<span style="font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-synthesis: weight style; font-variant: normal;">    </span></span><span style="font-size: 9pt;">Приказ о приеме водителя на работу в данное предприятие</span></span></font></p>
 <font color="#262626"> <font face="Verdana"><span class="LineHeight1-5"> </span></font> </font> 
<p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify;"><font face="Verdana" color="#262626"><span class="LineHeight1-5"><span style="font-size: 9pt;">11)<span style="font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-synthesis: weight style; font-variant: normal;">    </span></span><span style="font-size: 9pt;">Иной документ, подтверждающий взаимоотношения водителя и предприятия</span></span></font></p>
 <font color="#262626"> <font face="Verdana"><span class="LineHeight1-5"> </span></font> </font> 
<p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify;"><font face="Verdana" color="#262626"><span class="LineHeight1-5"><span style="font-size: 9pt;">12)<span style="font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-synthesis: weight style; font-variant: normal;">    </span></span><span style="font-size: 9pt;">Список транспортных средств, полуприцепов, водителей.</span></span></font></p>
 <font color="#262626"> <font face="Verdana"><span class="LineHeight1-5"> </span></font> </font> 
<p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify;"><font face="Verdana" color="#262626"><span class="LineHeight1-5"><span style="font-size: 9pt;">13)<span style="font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-synthesis: weight style; font-variant: normal;">    </span></span><span style="font-size: 9pt;">Бухгалтерская  (финансовая) отчетность за последний год.</span></span></font></p>
